00:49:55,251 --> 00:49:58,154
KEUN-SUK HAD A BIGGER CONCERN...

1329
00:49:59,722 --> 00:50:01,490
I don't know. I'm kind of worried.

1330
00:50:01,557 --> 00:50:02,625
As you all know

1331
00:50:03,059 --> 00:50:05,027
I still don't get women.

1332
00:50:05,861 --> 00:50:07,697
- I hope I'll someday.
- I don't think it was on

1333
00:50:07,763 --> 00:50:09,265
- if you ask me.
- It's finally working.

1334
