she doesn't love you anymore.

1348
00:50:44,066 --> 00:50:45,167
Gosh, how sad.

1349
00:50:45,234 --> 00:50:46,535
STARTLED

1350
00:50:46,602 --> 00:50:47,903
It's a dual-edged sword.

1351
00:50:47,970 --> 00:50:51,607
Girls usually drop plenty of hints
on why they feel upset.

1352
00:50:51,674 --> 00:50:53,576
But guys usually think,
"There she goes again."

1353
00:50:53,643 --> 00:50:54,844
Girls obviously know

1354
00:50:54,910 --> 00:50:57,079
that guys can get fed up
if they say they're upset too often.

1355
00:50:57,146 --> 00:51:00,683
People around our age
have enough dating experiences, too.

1356
00:51:00,883 --> 00:51:02,685
So the girl told her man
she was upset for some reason.

1357
00:51:02,752 --> 00:51:04,420
Then he'd think,
"Darn, this is serious.

1358
00:51:04,487 --> 00:51:05,621
Here we go."

1359
00:51:05,688 --> 00:51:07,657
If he apologizes,
she'll go, "What for?"

1360
00:51:07,723 --> 00:51:09,291
If he apologizes again...

1361
00:51:09,358 --> 00:51:11,427
He was wrong to think "Here we go."

1362
00:51:12,161 --> 00:51:13,663
OH, NO

1363
00:51:13,729 --> 00:51:15,898
So men aren't supposed
to think at all?

1364
00:51:15,965 --> 00:51:17,800
We want you to think
about what upset us

1365
00:51:17,867 --> 00:51:19,568
- and try to understand us.
- Exactly.

1366
00:51:19,635 --> 00:51:23,472
We're trying to be accommodating
when we choose to apologize.

1367
00:51:23,539 --> 00:51:24,607
- You should ask...
- "Sorry."

1368
00:51:24,674 --> 00:51:25,675
No, don't say that.

1369
00:51:25,741 --> 00:51:27,743
Ask us what upset us so much.

1370
00:51:27,810 --> 00:51:29,679
But if I ask that, she'll go

1371
00:51:29,745 --> 00:51:31,681
"Babe, you always say..."

1372
00:51:31,914 --> 00:51:33,182
"I get it. I'm sorry about that."

1373
00:51:33,249 --> 00:51:35,551
But the way you said that
was just so...

1374
00:51:35,618 --> 00:51:36,652
So I shouldn't say I'm sorry?

1375
00:51:36,852 --> 00:51:38,354
Yes, that phrase is...

1376
00:51:38,421 --> 00:51:39,755
Well, let me put it this way.

1377
00:51:40,523 --> 00:51:42,324
Let's try roleplaying.

1378
00:51:42,391 --> 00:51:44,360
All right, then.

1379
00:51:44,560 --> 00:51:46,495
<i>So, this couple's been dating</i>
<i>for two years now.</i>

1380
00:51:46,562 --> 00:51:48,664
<i>They're at a café,</i>
<i>and the guy dislikes it.</i>

1381
00:51:48,731 --> 00:51:50,833
<i>But the girl loves taking photos</i>
<i>while out in a café.</i>

1382
00:51:50,900 --> 00:51:51,901
<i>Okay.</i>

1383
00:51:53,069 --> 00:51:54,336
Can you take a pic for me, babe?

1384
00:51:54,403 --> 00:51:55,404
Look, just like this.

1385
00:51:55,471 --> 00:51:56,906
SOO-JIN HOLDS A POSE

