00:51:57,239 --> 00:51:58,874
KEUN-SUK WANTS HER TO KNOCK IT OFF

1387
00:51:58,941 --> 00:52:00,910
Soo-jin, can't we focus
on our conversation

1388
00:52:00,976 --> 00:52:03,045
when we're at a café?

1389
00:52:03,112 --> 00:52:04,480
We take photos all the time.

1390
00:52:04,714 --> 00:52:06,916
I know that, but this café
has such an amazing ambiance.

1391
00:52:06,982 --> 00:52:08,350
Come on, take a snap for me.

1392
00:52:08,417 --> 00:52:10,553
But we visit cafés
with great ambiance every week.

1393
00:52:10,619 --> 00:52:13,222
This literally isn't the only one.
I want to rest a bit.

1394
00:52:13,289 --> 00:52:14,857
I want to rest a bit.

1395
00:52:15,691 --> 00:52:16,892
Go rest at home.

1396
00:52:16,959 --> 00:52:17,960
Fine.

1397
00:52:19,228 --> 00:52:20,663
I was just messing with you.

1398
00:52:21,263 --> 00:52:22,264
ICY

1399
00:52:22,331 --> 00:52:23,733
I was just messing with you.

1400
00:52:24,433 --> 00:52:26,702
It was just a joke.
Do you have to shoot daggers at me?

1401
00:52:27,136 --> 00:52:28,904
Come on, Soo-jin.

1402
00:52:28,971 --> 00:52:30,573
- Soo-jin, I was...
- You ticked me off for real.

1403
00:52:30,639 --> 00:52:31,640
