1404
00:52:31,841 --> 00:52:33,309
Did you see my face harden?

1405
00:52:33,809 --> 00:52:34,877
That was a genuine reaction.

1406
00:52:35,077 --> 00:52:36,712
I was playing the role of a passerby.

1407
00:52:37,413 --> 00:52:40,015
- But I got so startled...
- Were you playing a role?

1408
