1423
00:53:12,014 --> 00:53:13,849
Don't I look great, though?

1424
00:53:13,916 --> 00:53:15,684
I'm just messing with you.

1425
00:53:16,085 --> 00:53:17,920
THAT ONE'S PRETTY FUNNY

1426
00:53:17,987 --> 00:53:19,522
