WITH ALPHA GIRL SOO-JIN'S OUTBURST

1449
00:54:15,472 --> 00:54:17,507
But your gaze was really menacing.

1450
00:54:18,608 --> 00:54:20,944
THE KIND OF GAZE
HER BOYFRIEND MUST AVOID FACING

1451
00:54:21,011 --> 00:54:24,080
- A relationship isn't really over
- That was hilarious.

1452
00:54:24,147 --> 00:54:25,615
when you lose your cool like this.

1453
00:54:25,682 --> 00:54:27,250
- He's right.
- It becomes crystal clear

1454
00:54:27,317 --> 00:54:28,752
