1455
00:54:28,818 --> 00:54:30,287
- when you sneer at each other.
- What?

1456
00:54:30,353 --> 00:54:32,422
- A slightly bitter smile...
- When you sneer at each other?

1457
00:54:32,856 --> 00:54:34,124
SCOFF

1458
00:54:34,190 --> 00:54:35,458
A scoff like this means it's over.

1459
00:54:35,525 --> 00:54:37,027
- My gosh.
- In other words

1460
00:54:37,093 --> 00:54:39,162
you can lose your temper.

1461
00:54:39,229 --> 00:54:40,230
But if you go, "Sure, fine."

1462
00:54:41,298 --> 00:54:42,699
"There. Satisfied? Let's just eat."

1463
00:54:42,766 --> 00:54:43,967
Then, it's over.

1464
00:54:44,034 --> 00:54:45,402
THERE'S NOTHING BEHIND A CALM SNEER

1465
00:54:46,436 --> 00:54:47,437
You're right.

1466
00:54:47,504 --> 00:54:49,406
A FIGHT MAY BE AN EFFORT
TO SALVAGE A RELATIONSHIP

1467
00:54:49,472 --> 00:54:53,343
I don't think the three of us
have been alone like this so much.

1468
00:54:54,110 --> 00:54:55,612
- You got that right.
- Right?

1469
00:54:55,679 --> 00:54:57,714
A bunch of nuisances
have always been around us.

1470
00:54:57,781 --> 00:54:59,115
POUTING

1471
00:54:59,482 --> 00:55:01,351
WHAT'S UP WITH HIM?

1472
00:55:01,685 --> 00:55:03,019
Doesn't he feel

1473
