1485
00:55:28,311 --> 00:55:30,680
- Two, three, four.
- What song is that dance for?

1486
00:55:30,747 --> 00:55:32,749
- I told you. <i>Like JENNIE.</i>
- JENNIE danced like that?

1487
00:55:32,816 --> 00:55:34,484
Well, I'm JINNIE.

1488
00:55:34,551 --> 00:55:35,652
My version is <i>Like JINNIE.</i>

1489
00:55:35,719 --> 00:55:36,786
I'm Suk.

1490
00:55:36,853 --> 00:55:38,655
I'M JINNIE, I'M SUK

1491
00:55:38,888 --> 00:55:39,889
You can do this.

1492
00:55:40,890 --> 00:55:42,359
- Suk.
<i>- Woo, like Suk</i>

1493
00:55:42,425 --> 00:55:45,729
JINNIE, SUK, AND HYUK ALL START
THEIR DAY WITH HIGH ENERGY

1494
00:55:46,896 --> 00:55:49,666
HE'S STARTING HIS 40TH BIRTHDAY
WITH PROSTATE CARE

1495
00:55:50,500 --> 00:55:52,435
SINCE HE'S A YEAR OLDER NOW

1496
00:55:53,336 --> 00:55:56,706
HE'S PAYING MORE ATTENTION
TO HIS MORNING ROUTINE

1497
00:55:56,906 --> 00:55:58,308
LAST NIGHT'S ENSEMBLE

1498
00:55:58,375 --> 00:55:59,943
WITH THE EXCEPTION OF A CAP

1499
00:56:00,343 --> 00:56:02,012
GLANCES AT HIS REFLECTION

1500
00:56:02,379 --> 00:56:04,748
A NONCHALANT FIT CHECK
BEFITTING A 40-YEAR-OLD MAN

1501
00:56:04,814 --> 00:56:06,750
I think that's the case.
Even if the woman...

1502
00:56:06,816 --> 00:56:08,018
Did you all sleep well?

1503
00:56:08,251 --> 00:56:09,486
You haven't changed.

1504
00:56:09,919 --> 00:56:11,721
You guys are up early.

1505
00:56:11,955 --> 00:56:12,956
Of course.

1506
00:56:13,023 --> 00:56:14,557
So early...
Did you prepare curry again?

1507
00:56:14,791 --> 00:56:16,092
It's braised short ribs.

1508
00:56:16,893 --> 00:56:18,795
Daniel, check out
what Jae-hyeon made.

1509
00:56:18,862 --> 00:56:20,497
- Now, Daniel.
- Wow!

1510
00:56:20,563 --> 00:56:21,931
This is your second birthday party.

1511
00:56:22,766 --> 00:56:24,534
- Are you ready?
- This is incredible.

1512
00:56:24,601 --> 00:56:26,036
Are you ready or what?

1513
00:56:27,103 --> 00:56:28,138
Are you prepared?

1514
00:56:28,204 --> 00:56:29,773
- So neat, right?
- My gosh.

1515
00:56:29,973 --> 00:56:31,274
What's this?

1516
00:56:31,341 --> 00:56:33,476
Dang, what's all this?

1517
00:56:33,710 --> 00:56:35,045
What on earth?

1518
