1649
01:01:07,116 --> 01:01:09,953
IN THE MEANTIME, MEN ARE BUSY
GETTING READY FOR THEIR GROUP DATE

1650
01:01:10,887 --> 01:01:12,889
<i>The key is finding</i>
<i>the right look for the occasion.</i>

1651
01:01:14,290 --> 01:01:17,360
<i>To make a good impression</i>
<i>on the ladies</i>

1652
01:01:18,795 --> 01:01:21,764
<i>I decided to take a safe approach</i>

1653
01:01:21,831 --> 01:01:24,500
<i>and opted for a modern</i>
<i>and noncontroversial look.</i>

1654
01:01:24,567 --> 01:01:26,235
PRINCE'S STANDARD FOR "EASY"
IS ON ANOTHER LEVEL

1655
01:01:26,302 --> 01:01:27,503
SECOND PARTICIPANT
SHIRO

1656
01:01:27,570 --> 01:01:28,571
<i>If you think about it</i>

1657
01:01:29,439 --> 01:01:30,640
<i>nothing beats a clean finish.</i>

1658
01:01:30,707 --> 01:01:31,741
HIS THEME IS A CLEAN FINISH

1659
01:01:33,509 --> 01:01:35,712
A CLASSIC EXAMPLE
OF AN EFFORTLESSLY STYLISH LOOK

1660
01:01:35,778 --> 01:01:38,114
THIRD PARTICIPANT
WRITER CHOI

1661
01:01:38,715 --> 01:01:40,550
<i>I'm inspired by a college freshman.</i>

1662
01:01:40,883 --> 01:01:42,785
