1664
01:01:47,156 --> 01:01:48,224
Shall we, then?

1665
01:01:48,291 --> 01:01:50,026
All right. Let's go.

1666
01:01:50,093 --> 01:01:51,260
THE GUYS ARE READY TO ROLL

1667
01:01:51,327 --> 01:01:53,529
- Let's go.
- Wow.

1668
01:01:54,097 --> 01:01:57,700
Are you dressed as Bae Yong-joon?
You're giving Bae Yong-joon.

1669
01:01:58,401 --> 01:02:00,236
ARMED WITH THE NOSTALGIA
FOR THE EARLY 2000S...

1670
01:02:00,303 --> 01:02:01,771
All right.

1671
01:02:03,539 --> 01:02:06,743
THEY'RE READY TO WIN
THE LADIES' HEARTS

1672
01:02:10,513 --> 01:02:11,781
CRACKING UP

1673
01:02:12,515 --> 01:02:14,884
CACKLING AT THE GUYS'
