- I've got a sweater underneath.

1687
01:02:39,142 --> 01:02:40,843
- I'm all about the clean finish.
- Good job.

1688
01:02:40,910 --> 01:02:42,645
- Jae-hyeon is your type?
- Yeah.

1689
01:02:42,712 --> 01:02:44,113
What about you, Do-yeon?

1690
01:02:45,348 --> 01:02:47,550
LET ME SEE...

1691
01:02:47,617 --> 01:02:49,786
GETTING HIS HOPES UP

1692
01:02:51,154 --> 01:02:52,355
My vote goes to Jae-hyeon, too.

1693
01:02:52,622 --> 01:02:53,623
Jae-hyeon?

1694
01:02:56,592 --> 01:02:58,094
Great. You're all so honest.

1695
01:03:02,832 --> 01:03:04,467
