This is our final look.

1696
01:03:04,534 --> 01:03:06,335
Well, as for fashion

1697
01:03:06,402 --> 01:03:07,870
- you did a fine job.
- You look amazing.

1698
01:03:07,937 --> 01:03:10,206
- You put together a great ensemble.
- You're all killing it.

1699
01:03:10,273 --> 01:03:12,742
Keun-suk looks charming
in this relaxed look, too.

1700
01:03:13,009 --> 01:03:15,478
With the clean-shaven face
and this whole look

1701
01:03:15,545 --> 01:03:17,580
- Daniel looks actually younger.
- Yeah, definitely.

1702
01:03:17,947 --> 01:03:20,750
My inspo is a college freshman
going on a group date on campus.

1703
01:03:20,817 --> 01:03:21,818
College kids' group date?

1704
01:03:22,552 --> 01:03:24,153
- Get going already.
- Let's get going.

1705
01:03:24,220 --> 01:03:25,855
- We're running late.
- Hurry and grab your stuff.

