Why don't you leave your bag here?

1995
01:13:57,653 --> 01:13:59,321
- Okay.
- I can take it for you.

1996
01:13:59,388 --> 01:14:00,923
- Thank you.
- Take this.

1997
01:14:00,989 --> 01:14:02,391
