2013
01:14:30,886 --> 01:14:32,254
Are you Aurora?

2014
01:14:32,321 --> 01:14:35,190
- Yes, I'm Aurora.
- Why did you choose that nickname?

2015
01:14:35,257 --> 01:14:36,759
- How come?
- I'm curious too, Aurora.

2016
01:14:37,426 --> 01:14:39,328
It's because I want
to go see the aurora.

2017
01:14:40,763 --> 01:14:45,000
ROMANTIC VIBE OVERLOAD

2018
01:14:47,503 --> 01:14:51,240
I'm here to find a companion
on my trip to go see it.

2019
01:14:52,608 --> 01:14:53,609
TOGETHER?

2020
01:14:53,675 --> 01:14:55,077
- But about auroras...
- Yes?

2021
01:14:55,978 --> 01:14:58,013
You can go see them
and return on the same day.

2022
01:15:00,015 --> 01:15:01,784
WHAT A WET BLANKET

2023
01:15:02,050 --> 01:15:03,051
That's true.

2024
01:15:03,118 --> 01:15:04,453
- You might miss it.
- You might miss it.

2025
01:15:04,853 --> 01:15:06,722
ALWAYS THINK BEFORE YOU SPEAK

2026
01:15:06,789 --> 01:15:08,657
Have you been
on a pottery date before?

2027
01:15:08,724 --> 01:15:10,526
- I've tried group dates before.
- You have?

2028
01:15:10,592 --> 01:15:11,727
Yes.

2029
01:15:11,794 --> 01:15:13,028
What was it like then?

2030
01:15:14,129 --> 01:15:15,564
This is my best group date so far.

2031
01:15:16,565 --> 01:15:18,033
This is my best group date so far.

2032
01:15:18,700 --> 01:15:20,469
WE DID THE RIGHT THING

2033
01:15:20,536 --> 01:15:24,239
BY MAKING AN EFFORT
TO LOOK GOOD TODAY

2034
01:15:25,307 --> 01:15:27,376
Sounds like one of them
is close to your ideal type in men.

2035
01:15:27,776 --> 01:15:29,978
- I'm holding him close in my heart.
- Oh, my.

2036
01:15:30,679 --> 01:15:32,381
SHE TOOK A LIKING TO SOMEONE
FROM JUST ONE LOOK?

2037
01:15:32,447 --> 01:15:33,749
She's got someone in her heart.

2038
01:15:34,183 --> 01:15:35,184
GULPS

2039
01:15:35,250 --> 01:15:36,385
- I heard that, too.
- You did?

2040
01:15:37,252 --> 01:15:38,253
IS IT ME AGAIN?

2041
01:15:38,320 --> 01:15:39,655
A man in her heart...

2042
01:15:39,888 --> 01:15:42,524
Can you guess what AP stands for?

2043
01:15:42,925 --> 01:15:45,861
PLEASE TELL ME THE MAGIC WORDS
YOU HAVE IN YOUR HEART

2044
01:15:45,928 --> 01:15:47,329
Apartment?

2045
01:15:48,230 --> 01:15:49,598
Apartment?

2046
01:15:50,232 --> 01:15:51,767
PRINCE'S DIGNITY
IS CRUSHED BY "APARTMENT"

2047
01:15:51,834 --> 01:15:53,669
Why don't we hit a bar?

2048
01:15:54,403 --> 01:15:55,571
That's a reasonable guess.

2049
01:15:55,637 --> 01:15:57,372
I like your answer.

2050
01:15:57,639 --> 01:15:58,907
Make that your nickname's origin.

2051
01:15:58,974 --> 01:16:00,409
- Hey, we have someone new here.
- Hello.

2052
01:16:01,143 --> 01:16:02,978
- Hello.
- Hello.

2053
01:16:03,278 --> 01:16:04,980
- Hello.
- Hello.

2054
01:16:05,047 --> 01:16:07,749
Hi, it's nice to meet you.

2055
01:16:07,816 --> 01:16:09,618
CONFIDENT, FULL OF ENERGY
KOALA

2056
01:16:09,685 --> 01:16:11,320
- Hello.
- Hello.

2057
01:16:11,386 --> 01:16:12,688
- It's nice to meet you.
- Hello.

2058
01:16:12,754 --> 01:16:13,889
THE MOOD LIGHTS UP, TOO

2059
01:16:13,956 --> 01:16:15,791
We're keeping the jackets here.

2060
01:16:15,858 --> 01:16:18,327
- I'll take your jacket and your bag.
- You look like the manager.

2061
01:16:20,195 --> 01:16:21,196
Was that a compliment?

2062
01:16:21,263 --> 01:16:23,265
- It didn't sound like it.
- It was a compliment.

2063
01:16:24,466 --> 01:16:25,834
- Thank you.
- No problem.

2064
01:16:25,901 --> 01:16:26,935
THANK GOODNESS I DIDN'T ACT UP

2065
01:16:27,903 --> 01:16:28,971
- Koala.
- Yes?

2066
01:16:29,037 --> 01:16:30,873
- Hello... You're Shiro.
- Yes, I am.

2067
01:16:31,073 --> 01:16:32,341
Writer Choi of Gugi-dong...

2068
01:16:32,875 --> 01:16:34,076
Apartment?

2069
01:16:35,177 --> 01:16:36,245
Apartment?

2070
01:16:36,311 --> 01:16:37,446
AGAIN?

2071
01:16:37,512 --> 01:16:39,514
Let's just go to a bar already.

2072
01:16:39,581 --> 01:16:41,116
Just roll with it.

2073
01:16:42,651 --> 01:16:44,653
HIS RIVALS ARE ESPECIALLY DELIGHTED

2074
01:16:45,354 --> 01:16:46,355
It was a reasonable guess.

2075
01:16:46,421 --> 01:16:47,723
Just roll with it.

2076
01:16:47,789 --> 01:16:49,625
Right, so...

2077
01:16:49,958 --> 01:16:52,294
I run a speech school.

2078
01:16:52,728 --> 01:16:54,096
Your reactions are so...

2079
01:16:54,162 --> 01:16:55,931
What do you do at your school?

2080
01:16:55,998 --> 01:16:57,633
We help a wide range of people

2081
01:16:57,699 --> 01:16:59,034
from politicians
to job-seeking students

2082
01:16:59,101 --> 01:17:01,036
- Oh, the job-seekers.
- to aspiring announcers.

2083
01:17:01,336 --> 01:17:02,571
That's so cool.

2084
01:17:02,638 --> 01:17:05,707
- Totally.
- And I'd like to add that I find

2085
01:17:06,008 --> 01:17:08,443
a group date like this very novel
at my somewhat mature age.

2086
01:17:08,510 --> 01:17:11,613
I came here pretty excited.

2087
01:17:11,680 --> 01:17:13,515
I hope we can have fun together.

2088
01:17:13,582 --> 01:17:15,584
EVERYONE IS EXCITED
LET'S HAVE A FUN TIME TOGETHER!

2089
01:17:15,651 --> 01:17:16,818
Well...

2090
01:17:17,252 --> 01:17:20,756
I'm a Korean-Japanese translator
and interpreter

2091
01:17:20,822 --> 01:17:23,425
and I am also a painter.

2092
01:17:23,492 --> 01:17:24,726
- A painter?
- Yes.

2093
01:17:24,793 --> 01:17:27,129
- I graduated from an art school.
- Really?

2094
01:17:28,096 --> 01:17:30,799
- I'm so pleased to meet you.
- Seriously?

2095
01:17:30,866 --> 01:17:34,436
I actually studied
in a Japanese art school.

2096
01:17:34,503 --> 01:17:35,804
- Really?
- Yes.

2097
01:17:35,871 --> 01:17:37,973
- An art college?
- So...

2098
01:17:38,040 --> 01:17:40,075
- I see.
- Keun...

2099
01:17:40,142 --> 01:17:41,243
Keun-chan.

2100
01:17:41,610 --> 01:17:44,012
I'm dying to brag about meeting you
to my Japanese friends.

2101
01:17:44,613 --> 01:17:47,649
HERE'S THE TEA ABOUT MEETING
JANG KEUN-SUK ON A GROUP DATE

2102
01:17:47,716 --> 01:17:49,584
Gosh, I'm amazed.
It's lovely to meet you.

2103
01:17:50,052 --> 01:17:51,586
LIKEWISE

2104
01:17:51,653 --> 01:17:57,626
I've been working
in the beauty industry for 11 years.

2105
01:17:57,859 --> 01:17:59,661
Just last year

2106
01:17:59,728 --> 01:18:03,098
I launched my own business,
and I'm doing my very best.

2107
01:18:03,665 --> 01:18:04,933
GAZING FIXEDLY

2108
01:18:05,334 --> 01:18:06,868
OVERWHELMED

2109
01:18:06,935 --> 01:18:07,936
THE POTTERY DATE BEGINS

2110
01:18:08,003 --> 01:18:09,838
All right, we'll get you paired up

2111
01:18:09,905 --> 01:18:11,974
