2112
01:18:12,040 --> 01:18:13,542
The gentlemen
will take out their items

2113
01:18:13,608 --> 01:18:16,211
and the ladies will pick
an item of their choice

2114
01:18:16,278 --> 01:18:17,546
to get you paired up.

2115
01:18:19,181 --> 01:18:20,315
I'm having so much fun.

2116
01:18:20,382 --> 01:18:21,750
- My gosh.
- Gentlemen.

2117
01:18:21,817 --> 01:18:22,951
<i>The first group date in my life.</i>

2118
01:18:23,218 --> 01:18:24,553
<i>I so badly wanted to try one.</i>

2119
01:18:24,619 --> 01:18:26,888
<i>A group of people taking out</i>
<i>a personal item each.</i>

2120
01:18:26,955 --> 01:18:28,690
I'll open up the pouch now.

2121
01:18:29,725 --> 01:18:30,859
I wonder what's inside.

2122
01:18:31,960 --> 01:18:33,161
EXCITED

2123
01:18:33,228 --> 01:18:34,229
First off

2124
01:18:35,197 --> 01:18:36,765
we have these wired earbuds.

2125
01:18:36,832 --> 01:18:38,233
Wired earbuds.

2126
01:18:38,700 --> 01:18:40,569
NERVOUS FOR SOME REASON

2127
01:18:40,936 --> 01:18:41,970
<i>Dental floss.</i>

2128
01:18:42,037 --> 01:18:44,172
<i>- Is that an ointment?</i>
<i>- Here are your options.</i>

2129
01:18:44,239 --> 01:18:45,774
<i>They're all everyday items.</i>

2130
01:18:47,209 --> 01:18:48,210
WHO BRINGS THESE TO A DATE?

2131
01:18:48,276 --> 01:18:50,779
Here are your options.

2132
01:18:52,147 --> 01:18:53,148
Pretty cute.

2133
01:18:53,215 --> 01:18:55,751
- Adorable.
- What are those cute items?

2134
01:18:56,218 --> 01:18:57,386
What should I choose?

2135
01:18:57,452 --> 01:18:58,587
JIGGLYPUFF GOES FIRST

2136
01:19:03,625 --> 01:19:06,294
NERVOUS MEN'S GAZES
FOLLOW THE TIPS OF HER HAND

2137
01:19:06,361 --> 01:19:07,763
So this is how you feel
on a group date.

2138
01:19:08,196 --> 01:19:09,598
I get it now.

2139
01:19:10,098 --> 01:19:13,101
NERVOUS AND EXCITED

2140
01:19:14,803 --> 01:19:15,837
I'm going to choose...

2141
01:19:17,139 --> 01:19:18,473
the dental floss.

2142
01:19:19,274 --> 01:19:21,243
Please keep it with you.
Next, please.

2143
01:19:21,910 --> 01:19:25,147
WHOSE DENTAL FLOSS IS THAT?

2144
01:19:26,148 --> 01:19:27,449
- Well...
- Koala.

2145
01:19:28,316 --> 01:19:29,518
I'll choose this ointment.

2146
01:19:30,085 --> 01:19:32,521
- I'll take the earbuds.
- That leaves you with these.

2147
01:19:32,587 --> 01:19:34,423
AURORA GETS THE EARBUDS AUTOMATICALLY

2148
01:19:34,489 --> 01:19:35,624
I'll choose this ointment.

2149
01:19:35,690 --> 01:19:39,694
MEN'S FACES REMAIN INSCRUTABLE

2150
01:19:39,761 --> 01:19:41,063
All right, then.

2151
01:19:41,129 --> 01:19:43,732
Was it dental floss?
So, whose item is this?

2152
01:19:43,799 --> 01:19:44,800
WHO IS THE OWNER?

2153
01:19:47,135 --> 01:19:48,437
SNEAKS A GLANCE

2154
01:19:51,673 --> 01:19:52,741
Me.

2155
01:19:55,811 --> 01:19:57,779
You two have been matched.

2156
01:19:57,846 --> 01:19:58,980
JIGGLYPUFF, WRITER CHOI OF GUGI-DONG

2157
01:19:59,047 --> 01:20:00,082
Hello.

2158
01:20:00,148 --> 01:20:01,316
Hello.

2159
01:20:02,517 --> 01:20:03,852
I got butterflies.

2160
01:20:04,853 --> 01:20:06,054
