2161
01:20:06,655 --> 01:20:08,657
after guessing its owner.

2162
01:20:09,558 --> 01:20:11,493
"I want to see your beautiful smile

2163
01:20:11,560 --> 01:20:12,994
all the time."

2164
01:20:16,765 --> 01:20:19,568
"I want to heal
all your painful wounds."

2165
01:20:20,235 --> 01:20:23,205
That's the message behind my item.

2166
01:20:23,438 --> 01:20:26,475
"I want us to work together
on the tangled mess of life."

2167
01:20:26,808 --> 01:20:27,976
That's my message.

2168
01:20:28,276 --> 01:20:29,377
I get it.

2169
01:20:29,611 --> 01:20:32,247
You and your partner
must make an identical item.

2170
01:20:32,314 --> 01:20:34,483
Feel free to discuss it.

2171
01:20:34,950 --> 01:20:38,420
WE'RE MAKING A MATCHING ITEM?
THEY MOVE FAST IN DATES NOWADAYS

2172
01:20:40,455 --> 01:20:42,023
Are you good at crafting?

2173
01:20:42,090 --> 01:20:43,859
I love making new things.

2174
01:20:43,925 --> 01:20:45,260
- Really?
- Yes.

2175
01:20:45,760 --> 01:20:48,830
I'm all thumbs, actually.

2176
01:20:48,897 --> 01:20:51,500
- Really?
- I had no luck with rice cakes.

2177
01:20:52,000 --> 01:20:53,702
Why do I get the feeling
you'll be good at this?

2178
01:20:53,768 --> 01:20:56,204
I'm so jealous
that you have a talent.

2179
01:20:56,404 --> 01:20:58,306
